<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Clad" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Clad,</orth> clothed, drest: <cit><quote>c. in mourning black,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1585" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1585</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in that dimension grossly c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 5.244" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 244</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. in arms,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a woman c. in armour,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 5, 3</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the morn, in russet mantle c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.1.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 166</bibl></cit>.
